appDescription.message: S to razširitvijo uredite katero koli sliko v internetu.
appDescription.description: Edit any Image on the internet using this extension.

subHeadOne.message: Urejajte slike iz mape ali interneta.
subHeadOne.description: Edit Images from your folder or Internet.

subHeadOneDesc.message: Urejajte slike na kateri koli spletni strani [z razširitvijo brskalnika] v internetu ali naložite svojo sliko na naše spletno mesto, če želite urejati slike kot fotograf.
subHeadOneDesc.description: Do Image Edit on any webpage [using our browser extenion] on the internet or uplaod your image on our website to edit images like a photographer.

subHeadTwoDesc.message: Obrezovanje, obračanje, vrtenje, risanje, oblika, ikona, besedilo, filter maske, filter slike in številni napredni filtri.
subHeadTwoDesc.description: Crop, Flip, Rotation, Drawing, Shape, Icon, Text, Mask Filter, Image Filter and many advanced filter.

headF1Desc.message: Prilagodite svetlost skupaj s poudarki in sencami, da dodate kontrast.
headF1Desc.description: Adjust Brightness along with Highlights and Shadows to add contrast.

headF2Desc.message: Povečajte nasičenost za izboljšanje barv, zmanjšajte jo, da zmanjšate njihovo intenzivnost.
headF2Desc.description: Increase Saturation to enhance colors, decrease it to reduce their intensity.

headF3Desc.message: Povečajte Ostrenje, da dodate kontrast podrobnostim in črtam na fotografiji.
headF3Desc.description: Increase Sharpen to add contrast to the details and lines within your photo.
